<br />EDIT: Maybe it was <a href="http://nesdev.com/bbs/viewtopic.php?p=658#658" class="postlink">this post by tepples</a>? I'm too lazy to keep searching, but maybe it had to do with OAM being DRAM and all.
<br />
<br />EDIT 2: There is also <a href="http://nesdev.com/bbs/viewtopic.php?p=11925#11925" class="postlink">this comment by Memblers</a>, about demos that don't work (although the demos might not have worked for other reasons?). Anyway, I didn't know much back then, so these recommendations might have been enough for me to avoid those registers.</div>

